net.sf.freecol.server.ai

Class TransportableAIObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.freecol.common.model.FreeColObject
      • net.sf.freecol.server.ai.AIObject
        • net.sf.freecol.server.ai.ValuedAIObject
          • net.sf.freecol.server.ai.TransportableAIObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FreeColObject>, ObjectWithId
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AIGoods, AIUnit

    public abstract class TransportableAIObject
extends ValuedAIObject
    A single item in a carrier's transport list. Any Locatable which should be able to be transported by a carrier using the TransportMission, should extend this class.
    See Also:
    TransportMission
